name: The Last Tree (itch) (skullblocks)
description:
As all of the great trees of old has died in this world it's up to you to harvest the seeds of the future from the greatest of oaks.

Unfortunately this journey will be more hazardous than you thought as the tree has started to decay under your feet.

Will you be able to get down the tree safely or will all hope be lost?

At least the ladybugs are cute!

Created for 5 City GameJam 2019 by Joakim Karlsson and Jens Sundqvist!
